title: MODERN 2/2 TOWNHOME IN A FANTASTIC COMMUNITY, WAITING FOR YOU!
posting_body: ['Come and see this modern townhome in the much-desired Communication Hills community!', 'Dark hardwood flooring provides a warm and classy ambiance to this charming abode, while high ceilings add elegance!', 'Natural light bathes the interiors through large glass windows with transoms.', 'Light-colored walls and ceilings with recessed lighting create a refreshing space!', 'Upgraded kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a large island!', 'White shaker cabinets and drawers offer lots of storage space.', 'Plus, you’ll also have a walk-in pantry with built-in shelves!', 'Primary bedroom enjoys a walk-in closet and an ensuite full bath with a glass-enclosed shower, double-sink vanity, and a separate toilet.', 'Secondary room has a built-in closet and easy access to a full bath with a shower-and-tub combo.', 'This home comes with in-unit laundry, water softener, water filter, water heater, and smart thermostat for climate control!', 'This home is in a peaceful community in the heart of Silicon Valley!', 'Walking distance to the community park and hiking trails, nearby shops and restaurants, and just a few miles away from downtown, major tech companies, and San Jose Airport.', 'Lease Term: 12 months', "Deposit Amount: One month's rent", 'Pet Deposit: $500', 'Included In Rent: Trash Removal', 'HOME ID: 4f0d77e5f7935d44']
